      <div class="accordion-item-body-content">
        According to Anxiety and Depression Association of America (ADAA), Anxiety affects 40 million adults in the US age 18 and older. Depression also affects 15.7 million adults with same age range!
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="accordion-item">
