      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="accordion-item">
    <div class="accordion-item-header">
        I noticed on your resources page you put CBT (Cognitive Behavior Therapy) on your page, what is that?
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item-body">
      <div class="accordion-item-body-content">
        Cognitive Behavioral Therapy is a type of psychotherapeutic treatment which helps patients understand the thoughts and feelings that influence behaviors. 
